          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Design quality vs features</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <div class="mt-16 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 bg-purple-50 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is Squarespace or Zyro better for website building?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Squarespace (8.4/10) is better than Zyro (7.5/10) overall, particularly for design quality with excellent templates (9.0/10 vs 7.5/10). Squarespace is ideal for design-conscious users, photographers, restaurants, and brands where aesthetics matter most. Zyro is better for budget-conscious users ($9-15/mo vs $23-65/mo) who want AI assistance with content writing and simple website setup.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 bg-purple-50 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What is the price difference between Squarespace and Zyro?</h3>
